text: Diary of a Wimpy Kid is a series of novels by Jeff Kinney. Diary of a Wimpy Kid may also refer to: * Diary of a Wimpy Kid (book), the first book in the series * Diary of a Wimpy Kid (film series), a film series based on the novels * Diary of a Wimpy Kid (film), the first film in the series
